author: chirino
msg: - Changing the org.apache.activemq.qpid package to org.apache.activemq.amqp package.
- In an effort to be able to code share easier with the qpid team, un-did lots of the refactoring that moved

- the qpid message handling into an activemq package.  Most of the code that was not highly modified is now back under a org.apache.qpid package.  This should allows us to pick up patchs/updates from the qpid team easier.  Currenly that code is baselined from the 468240 revision.
